{"tid":2125862,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"網民再傳新片 「廈溪」白Tee男7.21元朗站持刀恐嚇","createTime":"2020-07-26T13:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T13:47:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"791b5f4965ac223ad1a94a3dc69d06aa22097fef","tid":2125862,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200726/FT5IOBLJU76EQDWANCNDK7L2CE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FFT5IOBLJU76EQDWANCNDK7L2CE%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLn%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=2934da50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FFT5IOBLJU76EQDWANCNDK7L2CE%2F&h=e7ae542a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200726/FT5IOBLJU76EQDWANCNDK7L2CE/</a><br />\n<br />\n大批白衣暴徙去年7.21元朗無差別襲擊市民，多條網上片段均顯示，無論是「雞地」、南邊圍村及元朗站的白衣人，不少都手持長棒或竹枝等。更有最新片段顯示，當晚元朗站更有人懷疑持短刀，揮動威嚇站內市民。事發時在現場的立法會議員林卓廷說，翻看片段才得知竟有白衣人疑持刀，令人感心寒，又說對警方7.21事件的調查進展不抱期望，「永遠都唔會時機成熟」。"},{"pid":"e33b2b38776e37c8e91c313f86a65d956e934ca6","tid":2125862,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a982b84349fac3624f2ace3dfd17ad7f3a8f7a","tid":2125862,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:15:58.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"bba33835415c39bb1417e270162c7718d94a63f2","tid":2125862,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"擠足一年牙膏"},{"pid":"a0a35b28c6f9bede0bf2ffb04b8a87ae26a90ed3","tid":2125862,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hk